              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Priority Support</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          
          <a href="/contact" class="w-full bg-primary-500 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-600 transition-colors duration-200 font-medium text-center block">
            Get Premium Plan
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Setup Included -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-200 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Setup included:</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          WordPress migration, DNS configuration, security hardening, and performance optimization. 
          *Staging environment included if design services taken up with Connect. 
          *Migration Assistance compulsory - £250.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What's Included Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-black mb-6">
          What's included in every hosting plan
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          No matter which plan you choose, you'll get these essential hosting features 
          that keep your WordPress site fast, secure, and reliable.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg">
          <div class="bg-primary-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Lightning Fast Performance</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            SSD storage, advanced caching, and Cloudflare CDN integration 
            ensure your WordPress site loads in milliseconds.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg">
          <div class="bg-primary-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Enterprise Security</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Free SSL certificates, daily automated backups, and advanced 
            WordPress security hardening to protect your site.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg">
          <div class="bg-primary-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Professional Management</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Automatic WordPress core and plugin updates, 24/7 uptime monitoring, 
            and migration assistance included.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg">
          <div class="bg-primary-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Performance Monitoring</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Real-time performance monitoring and monthly reports to track 
            your site's speed and uptime performance.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg">
          <div class="bg-primary-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
            </svg>
